        </p>

        <ul class="bullets">
          <li>✔ No experience needed</li>
          <li>✔ Beginner-friendly simple model</li>
          <li>✔ Mobile accessible</li>
          <li>✔ Works in spare time</li>
          <li>✔ Free to learn</li>
